{"tid":576341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校園更安全？肯塔基州校區准教師佩槍","createTime":"2018-02-28T21:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T00:45:08.000Z","uid":132859,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ddde262e517de4972302e6b068f61f00de669230","tid":576341,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:50:39.000Z","msg":"美國肯塔基州派克縣（Pike County）校區，日前通過提案，校內老師近日內將可「隱藏攜槍」進入校園，以備不時之需。<br />\n<br />\n據報為保障校內師生安全，該校區周一投票無異議通過動議，將派出校方律師與當地警局商討，以利正式提出完整政策。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，有鑑於有鑿於近日佛州發生大規模槍案，會議上幾乎所有人一面倒支持校方人員配槍武裝自己，並且接受當地警方先行訓練。校方表示，還在研議多少工作人員需配戴槍枝，初步擬定一間學校至少一名，「這並非簡單的決定」、「不曉得會不會真的阻止槍案，但我想最終會將機率減到最少。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180228&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57885717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180228%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57885717&d=KAJfYNLaML4WSuj7codgJP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=06db4c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180228%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57885717&h=0787b915\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180228&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57885717</a>"},{"pid":"c962f9ccf2329520da412bd14424c98a4d28f14f","tid":576341,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:56:06.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"d35e961722fc04d3d2c87cb6d9d7f98680565a75","tid":576341,"uid":2854,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T22:14:02.000Z","msg":"訓練過嘅老師陀鎗有咩問題？<br />\n又唔係個個有。"},{"pid":"7f9794b34817eeca7143c73a3fe1124bbfed93a6","tid":576341,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T22:56:49.000Z","msg":"另一單新聞講<br />\n教師反鎖自己係課室 開咗一鎗<br />\n無人受傷"},{"pid":"1b623a223b18c081e547807053014739f6319e5d","tid":576341,"uid":125641,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T22:58:47.000Z","msg":"trump又贏"},{"pid":"b7bce20a94e5f3d8aecc3d1b0068bda9dd10cc9b","